title: New Jersey 2002 High Resolution Orthophotography 5000 foot Tile Index (MrSID)
name: New Jersey 2002 High Resolution Orthophotography 5000 foot Tile Index (MrSID)
description: These 5000 foot tile index polygons define the boundaries of individual orthophoto image files produced for the New Jersey Orthophoto Mapping Program 2002-2003. The tile scheme is in New Jersey State Plane coordinates, NAD83, in units of US Survey feet.

author.source: NJ Office of Information Technology, Office of GIS
